title: Gucci Medium GG Ophidia Tote
description: Gucci medium Ophidia tote bag in GG Supreme stitched black nylon and with black leather trim. Featuring silver-toned hardware, black GG logo at front, and dual flat top handles. The magnetic closure opens to a purple fabric interior with zip and patch pockets. Approximate dimensions: 36cm(Base-L) x 27cm(H) x 12.5cm(D), handle drop 24cm. Accompanied by Gucci dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
